rows.label: qst100606_msg0001
rows.name: *pant* *pant*

rows.label: qst100606_msg0032
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I! Not! Talk! To! You!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0002
rows.name: How should we approach this?

rows.label: qst100606_msg0003
rows.name: Scold him

rows.label: qst100606_msg0004
rows.name: Flatter him

rows.label: qst100606_msg0005
rows.name: Threaten him

rows.label: qst100606_msg0006
rows.name:
*pant*
Confess all crimes?

rows.label: qst100606_msg0011
rows.name: That make no sense!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0007
rows.name:
[ ML:Feeling kind=Anger  ] I am in middle of
repenting for crimes!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0008
rows.name:
*pant*
You think I look cool
running in wheel?

rows.label: qst100606_msg0009
rows.name:
Heh heh heh!
Bahn knows it.

rows.label: qst100606_msg0010
rows.name:
I am committed 100% to wheel!
It feel much more worthwhile
when you turn pulley yourself!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0030
rows.name:
You will stop me running on wheel?
What you mean?

rows.label: qst100606_msg0033
rows.name:
Replace wheel with harsher sentence?!
Bahn become pet for rowdy kids?!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0041
rows.name:
[ ML:Feeling kind=Anger  ] No! Please!
Anything but that!!!
*pant*

rows.label: qst100606_msg0034
rows.name:
Running on wheel just
starting to get fun...

rows.label: qst100606_msg0012
rows.name:
*pant*
You say Bahn-sama dishonest character
despite engaging in honest labor?

rows.label: qst100606_msg0027
rows.name:
I know I am bad guy.
Do not need you to tell me!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0028
rows.name:
*pant* *pant* *pant*
Bahn tired!
Stop bothering me!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0029
rows.name:
*pant*
If I help you open treasure trove, the
sincerity paint me in good light?

rows.label: qst100606_msg0013
rows.name:
Sincerity is not word that exist
in Bahn-sama's vocabulary.
That how I end up like this!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0031
rows.name:
[ ML:Feeling kind=Anger  ] Pfft!
Meh meh meh.
Stop bothering me!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0014
rows.name:
Huh?
You stop Bahn running on wheel?
What you mean?

rows.label: qst100606_msg0015
rows.name:
You dismantle wheel unless I tell you
how to open treasure trove?!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0016
rows.name:
Even though this is punishment,
I actually kind of enjoying it.

rows.label: qst100606_msg0019
rows.name:
[ ML:Feeling kind=Anger  ] Do not want to stop!
Bahn tell you how to open chest!
Just let me keep running!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0018
rows.name:
Just insert Ether Bottle, Filament Globe
and Key-Shaped Lever into chest. Then
chest will open!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0017
rows.name:
There! I told you. Now let
me run on wheel in peace!
*pant*

rows.label: qst100606_msg0020
rows.name:
Meh...meh...
If I confess all crimes, I get to
keep running on wheel?

rows.label: qst100606_msg0036
rows.name:
Mehmehmeh...
Is painful, but...
*pant*

rows.label: qst100606_msg0037
rows.name:
[ ML:Feeling kind=Anger  ] I not want to stop!
I explain how to open chest,
so please let me run!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0039
rows.name:
You need Ether Bottle, Filament Globe,
and Key-Shaped Lever.

rows.label: qst100606_msg0038
rows.name:
There, I told you!
Now no changing of Bahn's sentence!
Let me run on wheel!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0021
rows.name:
*pant* *pant*
Bahn-sama should be as honest as
honest labor?

rows.label: qst100606_msg0040
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Honest Bahn-sama would
no longer be Bahn-sama!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0042
rows.name:
I stay true to myself. Will endure
being pet of rowdy children!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0022
rows.name:
After rowdy kids play with Bahn,
Bahn will carry on running on
wheel while kids watch!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0023
rows.name:
[ ML:Feeling kind=Anger  ] Wheel is for Bahn's use only!
If someone else use, it get too
heavy and break!

rows.label: qst100606_msg0024
rows.name:
I have nothing to say to
fools who not care about
condition of wheel!
